; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
; ZONE 1 — STATIC
; Theme: machine spaces dormant, all threats are readable patterns.
; No Hunters, no Sentries. Sweeper/Pulsar/Wisp only.
; Teaching: dark mode, dark pocket, Sweeper timing, Pulsar rhythm.
; Flow: Spawn → Corridor A → Nexus Room → [Pulse Neck | Sweep Neck] → Terminal → Exit Hall → Exit
; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

; ─────────────────────────── PLAYER ───────────────────────────
[node name="Ship" parent="." instance=ExtResource("4")]
position = Vector2(450, 1100)

; ─────────────────────────── SPAWN ROOM ───────────────────────
; x:200-700, y:800-1400 (500×600). Safe zone, no enemies.
; DarkPocket inside teaches the mechanic before any threat.
; East exit y:1000-1200 leads into Corridor A.
; ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
