; ─────────────────────────── CORRIDOR A ───────────────────────
; x:700-1100, y:1000-1200 (400×200). First threat: SweeperA paces left-right.
; DarkPocket at west end: enter it, wait for the cone to pass, sprint through.
; ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
