; ─────────────────────────── NEXUS ROOM ───────────────────────
; x:1100-1700, y:600-1600 (600×1000). Open space.
; WispA orbits the cover island at center — orbital threat while choosing a route.
; Two cover blocks create a natural obstacle for the Wisp to anchor to.
; Upper exit y:800-1000 → Pulse Neck. Lower exit y:1200-1400 → Sweep Neck.
; DarkPocket in SW corner: first real decision pocket (hide vs push).
; ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
