; ─────────────────────────── TERMINAL CHAMBER ─────────────────
; x:2100-2800, y:600-1600 (700×1000). Both necks converge here.
; PulsarC fills the center with rings. WispB orbits the north pillar.
; Two pillars create cover lanes — player must thread Pulsar gaps while
; reading the Wisp arc. DarkPocket lets them pause and re-read threats.
; East exit y:1000-1200 → Exit Hall.
; ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
